goal.tools.unittest.result

Class UnitTestInterpreterResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • goal.tools.unittest.result.UnitTestInterpreterResult

  • public class UnitTestInterpreterResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Result of running the UnitTestInterpreter for a single agent. Includes the agent's test and any unexpected exceptions thrown during the execution of the test. Can be considered passed if no exceptions were thrown and the test result passed. Note that an agent may not have had a test.
    Author:
    mpkorstanje
